Class ReleaseFolders

java.lang.Object
  es.eucm.eadandroid.common.auxiliar.ReleaseFolders

public class ReleaseFolders
extends Object

The only purpose of this class is to keep the path of the folders and files which will be in the release in a common place for both engine and editor
